Package: linux-headers-grouper
Architecture: armhf
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-headers-${kernel-abi-version}-grouper 
Description: Linux kernel headers for the Nexus7 (grouper).
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel headers available
 for Nexus7 (grouper).

