Recommends: linux-firmware-grouper
Description: Linux kernel image for the Nexus7 (grouper).
 This package will always depend on the latest kernel image available
 for Nexus7 (grouper).

Package: linux-grouper
Architecture: armhf
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-image-grouper (= ${source:Version}), linux-headers-grouper (= ${source:Version})
Description: Complete Linux kernel for the Nexus7 (grouper).
 This package will always depend on the latest complete Linux kernel available
 for Nexus7 (grouper).

